{"name":"Мастерство магии","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>17-й уровень, умение домена магии</em></p><p>Вы выбираете четыре заклинания из списка заклинаний волшебника, по одному следующих уровней: 6-й, 7-й, 8-й и 9-й. Добавьте их в список доменных заклинаний. Как и все доменные заклинания, они всегда подготовлены и для вас считаются заклинаниями жреца.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Cleric 17 (Arcana)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-pentagon-orange.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"SCAG","hash":"arcane%20mastery_cleric_phb_arcana_scag_17_scag","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.i0UVzi5H0NyH36Yi"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668487182585,"modifiedTime":1668487519353,"lastModifiedBy":"XfGBpRnEldwS51r8"},"_id":"i0UVzi5H0NyH36Yi","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XfGBpRnEldwS51r8":3}}
{"name":"Многогранный ловкач","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>13-й уровень, умение мистического ловкача</em></p><p>Вы получаете возможность отвлекать цель своей @Compendium[lomeo-dnd5e-phantom.zaklinaniya-srd-phantom.4Vn1dTQyVyR3PK23]{Волшебной рукой [Mage hand]}. В свой ход вы бонусным действием можете обозначить существо в пределах 5 футов от руки, наложенной этим заклинанием. Если вы так делаете, то до конца этого хода совершаете броски атаки по этому существу с преимуществом.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Rogue 13 (Arcane Trickster)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/sundries/scrolls/scroll-bound-green.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"versatile%20trickster_rogue_phb_arcane%20trickster_phb_13_phb","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668445337493,"modifiedTime":1668446210605,"lastModifiedBy":"XfGBpRnEldwS51r8"},"_id":"i7tfUsdHEkjf6QCU","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XfGBpRnEldwS51r8":3}}
